title: Train smashes into van and car stuck on tracks in Pawnee, Oklahoma
description: The moment a train smashes into a car and van stuck on tracks in Pawnee, Oklahoma. Local police say the drivers of both vehicles tried to cross despite sings and barricades warning them not to cross. The drivers got out before the train arrived. #train #crash #traincrash #trains #railway

title: Nationals party room votes to scrap net zero emissions target
description: The Nationals have voted to scrap their policy of net zero emissions by 2050. Leader David Littleproud says the party will instead develop a "better, cheaper, fairer way" to reduce Australia's emissions. #auspol #nationals #davidlittleproud #netzero #climatechange
